
stellar-dust-storm-start-announcement = A dust storm is passing through sector space shortly, please refrain from extended exposure and check all external fixtures and hardpoints for damages once it has passed.
stellar-dust-storm-warning-announcement = It is estimated that the dust storm will pass out of sector space shortly, please remain indoors until it is confirmed to have passed.
stellar-dust-storm-end-announcement = The dust storm has passed out of sector space, it is now entirely safe to be outside your ships, and it is recommended for all crews to check their ships externals for damage.
